articles.title: New Year's Eve celebrations welcome 2026 around the world. See the photos. - CBS News
articles.description: New Zealand and Australia were among the first to welcome 2026, but in Sydney and some other cities, the festivities are tinged by grief.
articles.content:
Around the world, 2026 has begun to arrive. Crowds across the globe have gathered to ring in the new year, often accompanied by increased security measures.
